item.dc:creator: @WaleedScape WaleedScape
item.description:
@WaleedScape wrote:

  1. open up your character file
  2. delete it
  3. login with the same user name
    4.open up the new char file
  4. paste everything else

Why u did this:
your character file might have been damaged when u edited sommit in server, if not,
it happens, happened to me, i did those 5 steps.
